Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来　小切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都要看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们与贤者之石对抗的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这愚者之石算是钦定不打算改啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:40.59,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(593,300)\pos(950,420.667)}第八话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:40.59,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(593,300)\pos(950,477.667)}往昔明日　一念之隙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒畅无比沁人心脾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.47,0:02:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到石头的人这口气就是不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来艾尔芙娜茵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三下五除二过把水就闪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(622,666.333)}辉石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为使蒙尘的奇迹再度绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为对抗手段的湮灭屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以愚者之石的特性使贤者之石失效的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:02:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以将胜机紧握手中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此　首先也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克利斯　有经外务省转达给你的消息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消息？给我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴尔韦德那对姐弟想在回国前见你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思　帮我回掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴尔韦德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你把斯提芬的腿给…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　是我打的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克利斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去就是过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出的选择覆水难收
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此　可如此逃避下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕是当务之急也无从全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肺腑之言感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音　你现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　看来都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父　冷不丁得什么事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员到训练室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,训练？大叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚者之石都已经找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这又是唱哪出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按电影套路说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区一块石头就想大团圆结局了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有话就用拳头说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设立祭坛的仪式　进行得挺顺利的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是设立作为控制中枢的大祭坛所需的生命能量不够充足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么进行生祭不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两位任选其一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:05:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,补充设立祭坛的能量缺口应该是足够的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以那完美肉体炼制的生命能量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,局长　你到底是有多人渣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出选择吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以你的正义…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普雷拉蒂修复得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很顺利哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然多花了点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心怀同样梦想的同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错　伤害同伴的家伙绝不原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心意已决
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,训练程序　开始运行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和小切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要歌声能够同步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Zababa之刃来者不拒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算如此　这也太孩子气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次就特别由我下场陪你们训练
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不许跟我客气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不会手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底要怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对人下手心里还是会犹豫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手到底算不算人这个很成问题Death
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父　请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特训笨蛋你别真上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要一味横冲直撞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令这是打算以拳交心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教我们什么道理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但首先…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我胸中的烈马早已激昂难耐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止吧大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算数量再多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能集中打击也是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切记「心意一体」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆震
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是令贤者之石无效的手段而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧　热身都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那算是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来才是动真格的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七大行星以及七律音阶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这璀璨星空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宛如演绎美妙乐章的谱面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开天辟地的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快点选可要来不及咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要献祭哪位的生命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来令人在意的还是Symphogear啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总不能劳烦仪式的主角和伤病号吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可有什么妙计吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要努力到花颜折损的强敌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我说过不想再撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次就由我去攻其不备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的　连夜赶工在里面加入了湮灭屏障系统
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外形上没有什么区别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下就不会输给贤者之石了Death
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来　翼和克利斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经提前交给她们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像今天与旧识有约
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们坐今天晚上的航班回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在回去之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是想和你知会一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手术的效果很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是可以马上开始康复训练
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还想再多看看没有内战的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还有很多等着姐姐回去的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她决定继承令尊令堂的遗志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去援助失去了家庭与亲人的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继承爸爸妈妈的遗志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在刚才搬运的援助物品里有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸　妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我　索尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行　太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都怪索尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不能怪索尼娅姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这正谈事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alca-NOISE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在第七区监测到Alca-NOISE的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天羽羽斩与Ichaival请立即进行应对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:11:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,响她们正赶往现场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你们诱导民众避难
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位赶快去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好给我发泄心中不快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:19.44,IN_Y_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}Killter ichaival tron
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引蛇出洞轻而易举
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与敌方炼金术师开始交战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　孤身前来作战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佯攻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会是声东击西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音　别让敌人接近建筑物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面还有人没来得及避难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上蹿下跳得…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人好像不像嘴上那么坏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不讨厌你　但还是杀掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吧　克利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来太晚了吧　笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉　月读　晓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔我们也要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的　现在开始大反攻Death
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.18,0:14:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢　现在开始大反攻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐　调
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(940,666.333)}Unison
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红刃Shul-shagana与碧刃Igalima的合唱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普雷拉蒂以身犯险让我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要格外注意这两位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给人看扁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个距离飞行道具便无用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意料外的武斗派
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先下一城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我们两个Death
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被关起来了Death
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是无法找出中心的控制机关的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能靠蛮力强行突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的特训
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么还在这
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯提芬的轮椅卡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉呢　把你们卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:16:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会马上送你们一块儿上西天的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗急了上墙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候克利斯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在我也救了克利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去腿的过去是无法改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这个瞬间是可以改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来也一定同样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯提芬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐和克利斯你们全给过去束缚住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会用这双腿迈步向前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐和克利斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓励的话都说给你到这份上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也不能一直这么画地为牢固步自封了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但看你一扫阴霾就原谅你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,临阵磨枪使得出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题　正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交头接耳什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,IGNITE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(528,666.333)}Lapis Philosophicus
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沐浴着贤者之石的光辉为什么还能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是以前的Symphogear了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(400,666.333)}Unison
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是合唱　不是只有Zababa之刃才可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已确认愚者之石引发的湮灭反应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,IGNITE没有被解除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来顺利解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phonic Gain呈几何级上升
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(642,666.333)}Unison
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是合唱的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(662,666.333)}Unison
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调和切歌的合唱非常强力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以很可能会被敌人分隔开来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要只依靠Gear的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做到不论是什么样的组合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都能戮力同心　将歌声同步起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(700,666.333)}Unison
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羁绊的合唱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(578,666.333)}Lapis
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(938,666.333)}Unison
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅封印了贤者之石的光辉　还能合唱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能让圣日耳曼她们对付这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不能倒在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此高的能量输出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是想同归于尽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的魅力　一触即爆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用战胜当下的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解决掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克利斯　玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧　大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勉勉强强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克利斯　有缘再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂且别过　后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被干掉了　消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡里奥斯特罗化为天穹繁星了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会　卡里奥斯特罗居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下省事了呢　去掉了一个选项
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用来献祭的是普雷拉蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好呢　也受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这人到底有多…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊　我就是人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的说法完全正确
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚当你个人渣　禽兽不如
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但男人不坏女人不爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:22:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是比肩旧日支配者的神之力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区人渣都做不了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又如何将其纳入囊中
